{"title":"ARC AugmentedRenalClearance","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Nefrología/ARC AugmentedRenalClearance iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Augmented\\NRenal Clearance\\N(ARC)","guid":"x18u6mVqNH_qkgvyRM5YSQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definición","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"CrCl medido >130 mL/min/1.73m2 en hombres","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"CrCl medido >120 mL/min/1.73m2 en mujeres","guid":"f-t5LwYWtkD7tyfL2qwhGw","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Fenómeno de eliminación renal SUPRAFISIOLÓGICA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Descrito por Udy et al. 2010 → término acuñado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"\"EL ELEFANTE EN LA UCI\" → frecuente pero subdiagnosticado","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"Prevalencia en UCI general → 20-65%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"Prevalencia por\\Npoblación específica","guid":"vHFW4c-jp47wS2g_4-BC_w","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Trauma → 34-65%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"TEC severo → hasta 85%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"HSA → hasta 100% (cohortes pequeñas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"9","text":"Sepsis → 25-55%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"9","text":"Quemados → frecuente (datos limitados)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"9","text":"Neurocríticos → 55.5% (Ye et al. 2025)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"9","text":"Pacientes oncológicos UCI → 32% (Nazer et al. 2021)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"7","text":"CrCl medio en pacientes con ARC → 170-300+ mL/min","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"7","text":"Ocurre generalmente PRIMERA SEMANA de ingreso UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"7","text":"Duración variable → 1 día a 3+ semanas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"MECANISMO EXACTO NO COMPLETAMENTE DEFINIDO","guid":"JTedDhyCRYN3kW5XhvYd0w","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"Respuesta inflamatoria\\Nsistémica (SIRS)","guid":"aIvKiPA0ZeudkjbdRKHNQw","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"↑ citoquinas y mediadores proinflamatorios","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"Vasodilatación sistémica → ↑ flujo renal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"20","text":"Estado\\Nhiperdinámico","guid":"k9wXprguiOZOIlkdusjUhg","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"↑ gasto cardíaco → ↑ perfusión renal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"↑ filtración glomerular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"25","text":"Alteración secreción/reabsorción tubular","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"20","text":"Respuesta endógena\\Nal estrés crítico","guid":"x9xCIZsEpSKiYTbqJLDvfw","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"↑ metabolismo → ↑ producción de solutos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"Alteraciones neurohormonales","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"20","text":"Factores\\Niatrogénicos","guid":"b8LzUme2eqmYmqqh6Vgn1Q","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Resucitación con fluidos agresiva → ↑ volumen intravascular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"Soporte vasopresor → ↑ presión de perfusión renal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"Nutrición → ↑ carga de solutos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"20","text":"Reserva\\Nfuncional renal","guid":"SIbznBTv5zmNo4fk3Qc8cA","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"Reclutamiento de nefronas de reserva","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"Hiperfiltración compensatoria","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"0","text":"Factores\\Nde riesgo","guid":"7J2ppQ8ycuLJXhO9QMCwcA","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"PRINCIPALES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"Edad JOVEN (<56 años) → PRINCIPAL predictor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"Sexo masculino","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"40","text":"Trauma (politrauma, TEC, quemaduras)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"40","text":"Sepsis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"40","text":"Lesión neurológica severa (TEC, HSA)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"39","text":"Asociados","guid":"","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Menor severidad de enfermedad (SOFA/APACHE II bajos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"Creatinina sérica BAJA (<0.7 mg/dL) → SOSPECHA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"Cistatina C BAJA → correlación negativa (r = -0.336)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"46","text":"Pocas comorbilidades","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"46","text":"Neutropenia febril","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"39","text":"CONSIDERACIÓN\\NGERIÁTRICA","guid":"EB1i7eeT5sUv5R9-m8Qt9g","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"MENOS FRECUENTE en >65 años → pero NO EXCLUIDO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"Edad es factor protector → ↓ reserva renal con envejecimiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"Sarcopenia → creatinina sérica falsamente baja → CONFUSOR","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"52","text":"AM con buena reserva funcional + sepsis → posible ARC transitorio","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"GOLD\\NSTANDARD","guid":"ZlDof3DyScnZKsg47AqHIA","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"CrCl medido con recolección urinaria temporizada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"Recolección 8h → práctica y validada (Gerlach et al. 2023)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"58","text":"Recolección 24h → más precisa pero engorrosa","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"57","text":"LIMITACIONES de\\Nfórmulas estimativas","guid":"aRvsV0uH2nVYTuXHbxVWFA","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"Cockcroft-Gault →\\NSUBESTIMA CrCl en ARC","guid":"O-_GRFeu1u2e83BMPhSYfw","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"CG con peso ajustado = mejor en NO-ARC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"CG con CUALQUIER peso = MAL rendimiento en ARC","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"62","text":"CKD-EPI → mejor estimador global\\Npero INSUFICIENTE en ARC","guid":"tTZVLdVeD2XcvaJKc1g4gw","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"Bias de 44-56 mL/min en pacientes con ARC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"Cutoff eGFR-CKD-EPI ≥84 mL/min → sensibilidad para screening","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"62","text":"Creatinina sérica NORMAL NO descarta ARC","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"57","text":"Score ARCTIC\\N(Barletta et al. 2017)","guid":"g87BjQTi4P6oAt2K4LZaMA","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"Augmented Renal Clearance in Trauma Intensive Care","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"Variables","guid":"","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"Categorías de edad (<56a y 56-75a)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"Creatinina sérica <0.7 mg/dL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"Sexo masculino","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"70","text":"Rango → 0-9 puntos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"70","text":"Cutoff ≥6 → mejor balance S/E","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"70","text":"ROC 0.81 (p<0.001)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"70","text":"LIMITACIÓN → especificidad <0.7","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"70","text":"Validado externamente en trauma\\N(Jabamikos et al. 2022)","guid":"DSg7-v5eI7zEySMZyxLupg","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"S 93.1% / E 41.6% (trauma)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"S 87.5% / E 49.6% (médico/quirúrgico)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"70","text":"Aplicabilidad fuera de trauma → datos limitados","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"57","text":"Score ARC\\N(Udy et al.)","guid":"FUtSkXJgAerX7FoeXl0gyw","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Variables → edad, CrSérica, uso DVA, diagnóstico trauma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"Complementario al ARCTIC","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"57","text":"Algoritmo práctico\\Nde sospecha","guid":"RdrHvnDiAq4SxB8E2Uuy_w","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"Paciente UCI + joven + CrS baja + trauma/sepsis → SOSPECHAR","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"87","text":"Respuesta terapéutica inadecuada a ATB → MEDIR CrCl","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"87","text":"Solicitar recolección urinaria 8h → calcular CrCl real","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"0","text":"Implicaciones\\NFarmacológicas","guid":"WNuSeEcLY0PsR3o_nEUKLg","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"CONCEPTO CENTRAL","guid":"","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"Fármacos hidrofílicos de eliminación renal → ↑ clearance","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"→ Niveles subterapéuticos → FRACASO terapéutico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"92","text":"→ Riesgo de resistencia antimicrobiana","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"91","text":"ANTIMICROBIANOS\\N→ mayor impacto clínico","guid":"-cMweJ072rpgqn6_avKy4Q","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"Beta-lactámicos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"Piperacilina/tazobactam → infusión EXTENDIDA (4h)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"Meropenem → infusión EXTENDIDA (3h)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"97","text":"Cefepime → infusión EXTENDIDA (4h)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"97","text":"Cefiderocol → dosis aumentada si CrCl >120 mL/min (ficha técnica)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"97","text":"Cefazolina → considerar ajuste","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"96","text":"Vancomicina","guid":"","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"Solo 10.8% alcanza nivel terapéutico día 1 con dosis estándar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"51.6% nivel terapéutico día 3 → SUBDOSIFICACIÓN significativa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"103","text":"Clearance de vancomicina correlaciona con CrCl","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"103","text":"→ Dosis mayores + TDM estrecho","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"103","text":"AUC/MIC como target PK/PD preferido","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"96","text":"Aminoglicósidos → ajuste histórico reconocido desde 1970s","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"96","text":"Teicoplanina → necesita carga 800mg q12h x3 en ARC (Hu et al. 2022)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"96","text":"Daptomicina → considerar 12 mg/kg en bacteriemia/endocarditis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"96","text":"Linezolid → afectado por ARC (eliminación renal ~30%)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"91","text":"ANTICONVULSIVANTES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"Levetiracetam → eliminación renal >90%","guid":"","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"↓ niveles significativos en ARC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"114","text":"→ Dosis mayores + TDM","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"113","text":"Fenitoína → menor impacto (hepática)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"91","text":"ANTICOAGULANTES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"Enoxaparina →\\Neliminación renal","guid":"6haDzssujcjHlmCImD3KAA","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"↓ niveles anti-Xa en ARC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"119","text":"→ Monitorizar anti-Xa + ajustar dosis","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"118","text":"Dalteparina → caso reportado de subdosificación en ARC (Deenen et al. 2023)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"118","text":"Edoxaban → afectado por CrCl alto","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"91","text":"SEDANTES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"Midazolam → metabolitos activos de eliminación renal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"124","text":"Rocuronio → parcialmente renal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"91","text":"OTROS FÁRMACOS\\Nafectados","guid":"0iFSBIb9vKY2CKt9hFG2zQ","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"Fluconazol → eliminación renal >80%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"127","text":"Aciclovir/valaciclovir","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"127","text":"Metformina","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"0","text":"Estrategias\\Nde Manejo","guid":"1bEe1iS6QNzatWkC53bvuA","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"Identificación precoz → screening con ARCTIC score","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"Medición directa de CrCl → recolección urinaria 8h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"131","text":"Ajustes de\\Ndosificación","guid":"8zT8Bh4k99izuPpT_OVOiQ","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"↑ dosis unitaria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"134","text":"↑ frecuencia de administración","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"134","text":"Infusiones extendidas/continuas de betalactámicos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"134","text":"TDM agresivo → vancomicina, aminoglicósidos, levetiracetam","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"131","text":"Programa institucional de ARC\\N(Gerlach et al. 2023)","guid":"vBnKRoAky1tP3DQJpfbqWA","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"Protocolo recolección urinaria 8h estandarizado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"Guía dosificación específica para ARC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"139","text":"Enfoque PDSA (Plan-Do-Study-Act)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"139","text":"Liderado por farmacéuticos clínicos de UCI","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"131","text":"Monitorización\\Nfarmacoterapéutica","guid":"WVDD0LCL0qd66WbJkMHLuw","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"Niveles séricos cuando disponibles","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"Respuesta clínica + microbiológica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"144","text":"Reevaluación periódica → ARC puede resolver","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClínicas","guid":"odnFp_2BhCc11MPLjmrnJQ","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"Creatinina sérica NORMAL o BAJA en UCI → NO significa función renal normal → puede ser ARC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"Sarcopenia geriátrica → CrS falsamente baja → confusor con ARC → MEDIR CrCl real","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"Si ATB aparentemente adecuados no responden → SOSPECHAR ARC antes de escalar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"148","text":"Betalactámicos en infusión EXTENDIDA → primera estrategia ante sospecha ARC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"148","text":"TDM de vancomicina con AUC/MIC → no solo valley → optimiza dosificación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"148","text":"Score ARCTIC ≥6 → solicitar recolección urinaria 8h para confirmar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"148","text":"ARC es TRANSITORIO → reevaluar función renal cada 48-72h en UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"148","text":"En AM con buena reserva funcional + trauma/sepsis → NO descartar ARC por edad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"148","text":"Cefiderocol → ÚNICO betalactámico con recomendación de ajuste ascendente en ficha técnica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"148","text":"Programa institucional farmacéutico de ARC → mejora outcomes antimicrobianos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"0","text":"VER\\NTAMBIÉN","guid":"fHhQTrjss4YBAM6cYNrtFQ","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"→ Farmacocinética Geriátrica (Farmacología)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"→ Sepsis en Adulto Mayor (UCI)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"159","text":"→ Vancomicina TDM (Farmacología)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"159","text":"→ Betalactámicos Infusión Extendida (Farmacología)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"159","text":"→ Sedación UCI (Farmacología)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"159","text":"→ Fragilidad y Sarcopenia (Valoración Geriátrica)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"1. Cook AM, Hatton-Kolpek J. Augmented Renal Clearance. Pharmacotherapy. 2019;39(3):346-354.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"2. Ye X, et al. Prevalence and Risk Factors for ARC in Neurocritical Ill Patients. J Clin Lab Anal. 2025;39(11):e70047.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"166","text":"3. Jabamikos C, et al. Validation of the ARCTIC scoring system. J Clin Pharm Ther. 2022;47(10):1517-1524.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"166","text":"4. Gerlach AT, et al. Development of 8-h urine collections and ARC dosing program. JACCP. 2023;6(10):1132-1138.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"166","text":"5. Cucci MD, et al. Performance of CG in patients with and without ARC. Pharmacotherapy. 2022;43(11):1131-1138.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"166","text":"6. Nazer LH, et al. ARC in critically ill patients with cancer (ARCCAN). Pharmacol Res Perspect. 2021;9(2):e00747.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"166","text":"7. Deenen S, et al. Treatment implications of ARC in COVID-19. Fundam Clin Pharmacol. 2023;37(5):1011-1015.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"166","text":"8. Declercq P, et al. Reliability of eGFR formulae: Focus on ARC. J Clin Pharm Ther. 2018;43(5):695-706.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"166","text":"9. Hu S, et al. High-dose teicoplanin for patients with ARC. J Clin Pharm Ther. 2022;47(10):1548-1555.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"166","text":"10. Rhoney DH, et al. Scoping review of ARC in pediatric patients. Pharmacotherapy. 2021;41(10):851-863.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":176,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Nefrología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Nefrología","filename":"ARC AugmentedRenalClearance iPad","id":"map_1296","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"ARC AugmentedRenalClearance iPad"}